    "description": "<p>Knights Synergy (S) Pte Ltd was established in 2002 as a specialist sub-contractor providing specialist consultation to clients in the field of explosives application. In the array of diversification, the company has broadened its job scope to a one-stop solution provider by enhancing the cutting edge technique to incorporate geotechnical ground engineering works such as micropile, shotcreting, soil nailing, rock bolting, pressure grouting, recharge, and pressure relief wells and Cross Passages Construction (NATM).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>In successfully managing and completing the various challenging projects throughout the years of operations in both drill and blast, and geotechnical fields, Knights Synergy has acquired reputable recognition from various clients and in the process has enhanced the quality of its services.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Knights Synergy’s diverse clients will attest to their professionalism and quality of services in the successful completion of multiple projects to clients’ satisfaction and in a timely manner for successful handover. This is attributable to the close working relationship which together with their client, creates value in overcoming ground challenges inherent in projects within a densely populated Singapore.</p>",
